data.description: ***$20,000 Seller Paid Concessions Towards Closing Cost***Welcome to one of the most beautiful homes in the Luxurious Gated Community of Eagles Brooke Subdivision. This 4 bedroom, 3 and a half bath home is located on one of the largest lots in the subdivision. It sits on 1 acre of land in a cul-de-sac with a privately fenced backyard that was made for entertaining. The exterior of this home has been kept in superior condition with beautifully landscaped yard, extended driveway for additional parking, and 2 car garage. The grand foyer welcomes you with high ceilings and open floor plan. This one-of-a-kind home was built with attention to detail. Large columns separate the living room and kitchen, but still provides a spacious open floor plan. Crown molding accents the wall and the floors are all engineered hardwood throughout the entire home. The chef's kitchen has a gas stove, double oven, granite countertops, walk in pantry, and plenty of cabinet space. The first floor also features an executive office, dining room, and media room. The second floor features a large loft area, 4 large bedrooms, jack and jill bath, and 2 additional full baths. The gorgeous owner's sweet welcomes you with double doors and is a getaway in itself. It's massive space and vaulted ceilings give you plenty of options on how to use the space. You can also enjoy the sunrise in the morning on the deck that is accessible through the owner's suite and bottom level deck. The owner's suite also has a huge walk in closet and spacious ensuite attached. Eagles Brooke is a desirable community that features a swimming pool, play area, and lake. Call today for your tour!
